    <title>Edit multiple object groups at
        <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20160531T151833+0200" comment="Feedback to SME: In search field, add what you&apos;re selecting, For example Select an object or Select a group.

See GItHub #171 https://github.com/dhis2/maintenance-app/issues/171
"?>once<?oxy_comment_end?></title>
    <?oxy_comment_end?>
    <para>The <emphasis role="bold">Metadata group editor</emphasis> in the <emphasis role="bold"
            >Maintenance</emphasis> app allows you to edit multiple object groups at the same time.
        You can edit the following objects types:</para>
    <table frame="all">
        <title>Object types in the Metadata group editor</title>
        <tgroup cols="2">
            <colspec colname="c1" colnum="1" colwidth="1.0*"/>
            <colspec colname="c2" colnum="2" colwidth="1.0*"/>
            <thead>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Object type</para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Available functions</para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
            </thead>
            <tbody>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Category option</para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry>
                        <para/>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para><?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20160531T101152+0200" comment="Lars submitted ticket for category option groups:
https://github.com/dhis2/maintenance-app/issues/168
"?>Category
                            option group<?oxy_comment_end?></para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry>
                        <para/>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Data element</para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Add one data element to multiple data element groups</para>
                        <para>Remove one data element from multiple data element groups</para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Data element group</para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Add multiple data elements to one data element group</para>
                        <para>Remove multiple data elements from one data element group</para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Indicator</para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Add one indicator to multiple indicator groups</para>
                        <para>Remove one indicator from multiple indicator groups </para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Indicator group</para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry>
                        <para>Add multiple indicators to one indicator group</para>
                        <para>Remove multiple indicators from one indicator group</para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
            </tbody>
        </tgroup>
    </table>
    <section>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>
        <title>Edit multiple objects in a group</title>
        <?oxy_custom_end?>
        <orderedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>Click <emphasis role="bold">Apps</emphasis> > <emphasis role="bold"
                        >Maintenance</emphasis> > <emphasis role="bold">Metadata group
                        editor</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Click <emphasis role="bold">Manage items in group</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Select an object group type, for example <emphasis role="bold">Indicator
                        groups</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Select an object group, for example <emphasis role="bold"
                    >HIV</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>In the left-hand list, select the object(s) you want to add to the object
                    group and click the right arrow.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>In the right-hand list, select the object(s) you want to remove from the
                    object group and click the left
                    <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20160531T130118+0200" comment="For SME: Auto-saved?"?>arrow<?oxy_comment_end?>.</para>
            </listitem>
        </orderedlist>
    </section>
    <section>
        <?oxy_custom_start type="oxy_content_highlight" color="255,255,0"?>
        <title>Edit multiple object groups in an object</title>
        <?oxy_custom_end?>
        <orderedlist>
            <listitem>
                <para>Click <emphasis role="bold">Apps</emphasis> > <emphasis role="bold"
                        >Maintenance</emphasis> > <emphasis role="bold">Metadata group
                        editor</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Click <emphasis role="bold">Manage groups for item</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Select an object type, for example <emphasis role="bold"
                    >Indicators</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>Select an object, for example <emphasis role="bold">ANC LLITN
                        coverage</emphasis>.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>In the left-hand list, select the objects group(s) you want to add the object
                    to and click the right arrow.</para>
            </listitem>
            <listitem>
                <para>In the right-hand list, select the object group(s) you want to
                    r<?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20160531T132847+0200" comment="Revise wording, maybe &quot;from which you want to remove...&quot;"?>emove
                    the object from<?oxy_comment_end?> and click the left
                    <?oxy_comment_start author="cecilia" timestamp="20160531T130118+0200" comment="For SME: Auto-saved?"?>arrow<?oxy_comment_end?>,</para>
            </listitem>
        </orderedlist>
    </section>
</chapter>